Dialogue: 10,0:01:47.18,0:01:48.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yu...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:50.38,0:01:51.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,ri...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:55.23,0:01:56.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayah.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:57.61,0:02:00.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Wujudmu sungguh mengerikan.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:02.54,0:02:05.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yuri? Kamu di sini?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:05.67,0:02:07.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu di mana?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:08.47,0:02:09.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yuri.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:11.29,0:02:13.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Malang sekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:14.99,0:02:16.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yuri.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:17.18,0:02:18.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yuri.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:19.22,0:02:23.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa kamu pergi dariku?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:24.01,0:02:28.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Rasa sakit dari menanggung\Nkekuatan yang besar,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:29.56,0:02:32.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,ketergantungan terhadap\Nyang bersifat material.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:32.86,0:02:37.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku paham penderitaan itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:38.21,0:02:40.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Persis seperti diriku.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:41.88,0:02:45.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah kubilang tetap di sisiku!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:47.03,0:02:48.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yuri.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:49.46,0:02:54.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Asalkan ada dirimu,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:55.39,0:02:57.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku tidak butuh apa-apa lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:59.10,0:03:01.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mencin...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:08.55,0:03:09.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa yang dia lakukan!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:17.85,0:03:22.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa, Yuri? Kenapa?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:22.19,0:03:26.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu mengkhianatiku, Yuri!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:26.19,0:03:30.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akan kubunuh kamu!\NDasar ja...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:36.20,0:03:37.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tubuh!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:39.11,0:03:45.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tubuhku!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:45.75,0:03:48.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Persis seperti diriku.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:00.26,0:04:02.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dasar sialan itu!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:02.18,0:04:04.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tubuh! Tubuh! Tubuh!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:04.69,0:04:07.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kilatan biru tadi itu apa.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.43,0:04:09.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan menghubungi kesatria.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:10.42,0:04:15.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini sudah waktunya tidur.\NSegera ke kasur kalian.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.95,0:04:17.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kepala Biara?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.33,0:04:20.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kepala Biara!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:20.58,0:04:22.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tubuh! Tubuh!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.66,0:04:29.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hukuman langit!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.17,0:04:31.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pak Eminescu! Selamatkan dirimu!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:31.95,0:04:33.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sedikit lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:33.67,0:04:35.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Padahal tinggal sedikit lagi!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.01,0:04:38.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Michaela, kamu tidak apa-apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:38.84,0:04:39.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:43.77,0:04:44.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Larilah!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.77,0:04:46.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tubuh! Tubuh! Tubuh!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.35,0:04:51.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Igor!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:52.47,0:04:53.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan mendekat!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:53.87,0:04:55.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Pergi dan tinggalkan aku saja!\N- Tidak mau!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:55.62,0:04:57.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan ke sini!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:58.91,0:05:03.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayah! Apa yang terjadi?\NBawakan pemadam api!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.10,0:05:06.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada Homare di sini!\NCepat lakukan sesuatu!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:09.11,0:05:10.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di kediaman utama ribut sekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:11.56,0:05:12.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada apa, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:12.89,0:05:14.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak tahu.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:14.70,0:05:16.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dunia sedang berguncang.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:16.84,0:05:19.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tubuh! Tubuh! Tubuh!\NTubuh! Tubuh!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.61,0:05:23.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayah!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.01,0:05:31.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tatsuma.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:32.26,0:05:34.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tuan Tatsuma, selamatkan dirimu!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:34.25,0:05:36.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,On! Nisomuba basaraun hatta!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:42.34,0:05:47.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dingin, dingin tapi tubuhku
Dialogue: 10,0:05:47.00,0:05:49.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,terbakar.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.22,0:05:51.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nekosuke!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.21,0:05:57.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apakah semua pertanda ini\Nmenuju ke hal ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:57.58,0:05:59.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Fujimoto!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:00.30,0:06:02.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dengar, para anak muda.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.06,0:06:05.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Evakuasi keluarga kuil\Nke kaki gunung dengan selamat.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:05.10,0:06:06.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.07,0:06:06.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Takezo!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:07.16,0:06:07.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:07.88,0:06:12.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu yang memimpin mereka!\NLalu lepaskan Yamantaka!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:12.14,0:06:12.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baik!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:16.24,0:06:17.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayah bagaimana?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.18,0:06:20.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan membantu Tuan Tatsuma.\NAku mengandalkanmu!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.49,0:06:21.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jaga dirimu juga!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:22.76,0:06:24.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kak Take.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.77,0:06:29.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ibu, Ibu...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.95,0:06:33.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita akan ikut para anak muda\Nuntuk turun gunung.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:33.88,0:06:34.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa kamu bisa?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:34.79,0:06:35.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Iya.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:35.51,0:06:37.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Gampang!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:37.03,0:06:38.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bisa.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.46,0:06:40.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian memang anak-anak yang baik.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:42.47,0:06:43.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tenang saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:44.30,0:06:46.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kakakmu ini akan melindungi kalian!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.54,0:06:57.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yoshi, sini pegangan ke pundakku.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:58.11,0:07:00.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak bisa, Nyonya Torako.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:02.03,0:07:06.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau terjadi sesuatu padamu dan anakmu,\Nnanti bisa dimarahi Nekosuke.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.62,0:07:11.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tuh, Ryuuji juga bilang iya.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.37,0:07:12.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:16.76,0:07:18.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kakiku sakit.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:18.98,0:07:20.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Beratnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:20.49,0:07:21.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Semuanya, bertahanlah!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:23.88,0:07:26.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Renzou, sudah, sudah.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.39,0:07:30.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mohon!\NBiarkan mereka istirahat sebentar saja!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:30.53,0:07:31.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan mengeluh!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:31.89,0:07:34.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita disuruh untuk turun gunung\Nsecepat mungkin!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.78,0:07:36.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dasar anak manja!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:36.19,0:07:38.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada api biru!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:50.25,0:07:52.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dasar bocah kurang ajar.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.40,0:08:02.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kak Take!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.53,0:08:09.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kak Take!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:15.01,0:08:17.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada laporan dari seluruh negeri\Ntentang meningkatnya keganasan iblis!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:17.97,0:08:20.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini pertama kalinya familiar\Njadi sulit dikendalikan!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.98,0:08:24.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa ini ada hubungannya\Ndengan pembunuhan bayi Satan itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:24.69,0:08:26.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Atau jangan bilang.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.49,0:08:30.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tuan Armumahel!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.00,0:08:35.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tuan Azazel!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:36.81,0:08:39.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ja-Jangan mendekat!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:39.75,0:08:41.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan, Lewin!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:41.15,0:08:42.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lepaskan, Osceola!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:44.28,0:08:48.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hebat!\NMungkin ini rasukan paksa dari Satan!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:48.33,0:08:49.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa yang sebenarnya terjadi?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:51.29,0:08:52.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nyonya Shemihaza!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:59.48,0:09:01.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Beliau bertahan...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:01.71,0:09:05.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Satan mulai bergentayangan mencari wadah.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:06.68,0:09:07.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ilya.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.47,0:09:08.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.52,0:09:10.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bawa Shiemi ke tempat berlindung.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:10.55,0:09:11.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baik!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:11.77,0:09:14.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan sampai terjadi sesuatu\Npada anak di kandungannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:14.43,0:09:15.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ibu?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.13,0:09:19.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku harus pergi!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.60,0:09:31.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aria sudah tidak efektif, mundur!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.93,0:09:32.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Paladin!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:32.85,0:09:35.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Para Doctor mencoba membawa Yuri Egin pergi.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.73,0:09:37.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cih, malah di saat sibuk begini.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:37.86,0:09:41.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hentikan mereka.\NMasih ada satu lagi di dalam perutnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.01,0:09:42.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau mereka melawan...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.35,0:09:44.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baik!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:46.02,0:09:48.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Palladion, Arc Knight siap bertempur!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:50.60,0:09:53.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Wanita dan anak di dalam kandungannya\Nhanya manusia biasa!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:53.62,0:09:55.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kami akan melakukan operasi!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:55.31,0:09:59.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak ada buktinya!\NKami diperintah membunuh kedua anaknya!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:59.30,0:10:01.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi, kalau terus begini, ibunya...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:01.63,0:10:05.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nanti juga ada jalannya!\NYang penting anaknya mati dulu!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:05.63,0:10:06.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,A...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.20,0:10:09.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunggu, sepertinya dia sudah sekarat.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:09.42,0:10:12.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lebih baik langsung dibunuh\Ndan masalah pun selesai.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:14.65,0:10:17.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,A-Apa-apaan kamu?\NSudah gila, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.74,0:10:20.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Justru kalianlah yang harus\Ndinginkan kepala dulu!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:20.95,0:10:25.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Belum ada perintah membunuh Egin.\NKalau seenaknya lagi, aku tembak.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.65,0:10:27.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada pengkhianat!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:27.09,0:10:30.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukan! Beliau hanya mematuhi\Nperintah Grigori!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.16,0:10:35.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yuri, apa kamu mendengarku?\NKalau terus begini, kamu akan dibunuh.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.53,0:10:37.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lahirkan dia kalau ingin hidup.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.45,0:10:42.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak apa-apa.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:42.82,0:10:46.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku hanya istirahat sebentar.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:46.82,0:10:47.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagus!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:00.57,0:11:01.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tizona.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:02.62,0:11:04.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Colada.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:06.19,0:11:07.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ulmodo.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:10.65,0:11:11.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Gintora!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:27.17,0:11:29.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terlalu cepat dan gesit!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:34.43,0:11:36.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagus! Sekarang!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.60,0:11:41.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah lahir!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:46.94,0:11:47.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:49.08,0:11:50.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia tidak menangis.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:52.05,0:11:53.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia mati suri.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.31,0:11:56.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Segera bawa ke ruang tindakan NICU!\NKalau tidak cepat, akan terlambat!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:56.84,0:11:57.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunggu!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.95,0:12:01.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Anak itu tidak boleh pergi dari sini!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:01.83,0:12:05.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Biar kami yang memastikan\Ndia mewarisi kekuatan Satan atau tidak!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:05.46,0:12:06.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak ada waktu lagi!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:06.52,0:12:07.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Serahkan!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.47,0:12:08.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:10.04,0:12:11.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia sama sekali tidak bergerak.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:11.99,0:12:14.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu, coba rangsang dia!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.20,0:12:14.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baik!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:16.97,0:12:18.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hentikan.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:18.85,0:12:20.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baik! Tidak ada reaksi!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:20.76,0:12:25.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Periksa warna matanya!\NKalau bersinar biru, berarti anaknya Satan!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:25.48,0:12:26.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baik!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:29.69,0:12:31.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mata kanannya berwarna hijau normal!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:32.39,0:12:33.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hentikan.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:33.80,0:12:35.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia bisa mati.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:36.11,0:12:37.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mohon.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:39.26,0:12:41.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Biar aku yang memastikannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:41.94,0:12:46.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi kumohon, serahkan anak itu padaku.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:58.89,0:12:59.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada celah!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:01.15,0:13:03.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kena! Ini saatnya!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:03.82,0:13:05.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kerja bagus, Loxley!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:06.51,0:13:07.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Napasnya...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:10.26,0:13:11.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kasihan sekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:15.45,0:13:16.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia bernapas!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:23.18,0:13:24.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ingin memeluknya?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:38.54,0:13:39.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tizona.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.72,0:13:40.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maxima Fuego.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:40.85,0:13:42.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Enkerei!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:14.21,0:14:16.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baru muncul sekarang, badut sialan?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:17.42,0:14:21.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Paladin telah gugur,\Nberarti Operasi Petir Biru sudah gagal!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:22.86,0:14:25.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mulai sekarang, biar aku yang ambil alih.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:25.85,0:14:29.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian para Doctor sudah tidak dibutuhkan,\Nsilakan mundur dari sini.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:29.77,0:14:30.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ba-Baik!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:31.63,0:14:33.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebagai Doctor,\Naku hanya bisa mengatakan ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:34.45,0:14:36.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mendoakan keberuntunganmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:36.57,0:14:37.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.74,0:14:40.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia mati?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:40.62,0:14:42.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak, dia sehat walafiat.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:43.40,0:14:44.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa rencanamu?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:44.51,0:14:47.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Menurutmu?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:51.00,0:14:52.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lihatlah.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.71,0:15:03.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bahkan pedang Paladin, Tizona pun tidak bisa\Nmenghancurkan jantung anak Satan.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:04.62,0:15:07.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau aku melawannya secara langsung,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:07.09,0:15:10.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,dampaknya akan menjadi bencana\Nyang lebih besar dari saat ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:11.95,0:15:12.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:13.48,0:15:15.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,dengan pedang itu...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:18.10,0:15:20.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukannya ini tidak ada isinya?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:20.67,0:15:22.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Justru itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:22.41,0:15:26.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebenarnya aku membuat pedang itu\Nseratus lima puluh tahun yang lalu,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:26.72,0:15:28.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,lalu memberikannya pada biksu muda.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:28.99,0:15:29.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hah?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:29.90,0:15:31.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Percaya saja!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.65,0:15:33.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dasar.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:34.19,0:15:37.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lagi pula tidak ada yang tahu\Ncara mengalahkan anaknya Satan.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.82,0:15:40.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi aku hanya melakukan sebisaku.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:44.02,0:15:44.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mundurlah.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:44.55,0:15:45.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baik!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.11,0:15:46.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pasang pertahanan yang paling kuat!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:46.77,0:15:47.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baik!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:50.14,0:15:53.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ikatlah kebenaran sebagai sabuk,\Nkenakan keadilan sebagai pelindung dada,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:53.80,0:15:57.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,doa sebagai helm,\Nkeimanan sebagai perisai,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:57.72,0:15:59.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan genggamlah pedang roh!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:01.64,0:16:02.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Shiro.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.93,0:16:05.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan melawannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:07.43,0:16:11.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mungkin dia hanya melindungi\Nkita dan dirinya.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.11,0:16:13.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Biarkan aku bersamanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:14.35,0:16:15.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian pergilah.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:16.38,0:16:17.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mohon!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:26.98,0:16:28.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak mau!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:33.17,0:16:35.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akhirnya bisa beraksi.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.61,0:16:42.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei, sarungnya juga berharga, tahu!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.56,0:17:14.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Shiro!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:17.56,0:17:20.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Zeuxo, plexaura.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:20.53,0:17:22.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cerceis, plouto.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:23.41,0:17:25.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Europa, eudora.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.43,0:17:32.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku memohon kepada...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.55,0:17:35.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tiga Ribu Putri Istana Oceanus.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:46.05,0:17:46.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sekarang!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:47.06,0:17:49.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oceanids Carousel!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.25,0:18:22.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Matilah!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:43.06,0:18:45.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bocah tidur saja!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:45.86,0:18:48.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sana!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:52.63,0:18:53.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.34,0:18:56.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jantungnya
Dialogue: 10,0:18:57.42,0:18:58.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,menyerap ke pedang.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:03.79,0:19:08.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar, pedang ini semacam\Npintu ke mana saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.71,0:19:14.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Gagangnya terhubung ke Gehenna,\Ndan sarungnya menjadi pintu.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:14.65,0:19:19.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ketika keduanya bersatu,\Nbisa menyegel iblis Gehenna.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:26.37,0:19:29.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Wah, setelah menyegel jantungnya,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:29.91,0:19:33.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,dia jadi terpisah dari sifat iblisnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:33.26,0:19:35.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maksudnya menjadi manusia?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:35.08,0:19:36.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:36.06,0:19:41.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bayi ini tetap manusia dan iblis.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:41.94,0:19:44.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lebih baik bunuh saja selagi dia anteng.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:44.62,0:19:46.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selama jantungnya belum dihancurkan,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:47.79,0:19:51.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,dia akan terus bangkit kembali\Nmeskipun kita membunuhnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:51.16,0:19:55.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selain itu, segel hanyalah sebatas segel.\NPasti ada batasnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:55.96,0:20:00.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dalam situasi ini, kita hanya bisa mengurung\Ntubuhnya secara semi-permanen
Dialogue: 10,0:20:00.09,0:20:02.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan terus menghancurkannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:03.54,0:20:05.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi dia juga manusia.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:06.54,0:20:12.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kepribadian macam apa yang akan terbentuk\Ndari manusia yang terus-menerus disiksa?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:13.56,0:20:17.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu ingin melahirkan\NSatan dan Lucifer yang kedua?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:17.74,0:20:19.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak bermaksud...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:21.48,0:20:23.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:25.30,0:20:29.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Demi mencegah hal itu, lebih baik
Dialogue: 10,0:20:32.25,0:20:35.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,kita mengembalikannya ke pelukan ibunya.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:37.81,0:20:39.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pak Pheles.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:43.02,0:20:44.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:47.69,0:20:51.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lebih baik jangan berterima kasih padaku.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:52.20,0:20:53.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Musuh baru telah muncul.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:57.03,0:21:00.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Api biru?\NBukankah jantungnya sudah disegel?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:00.68,0:21:03.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu bukan ulah bayinya.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:03.09,0:21:03.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:08.12,0:21:08.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan bilang.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:13.97,0:21:14.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Paladin!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:19.96,0:21:23.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,A-Ayah...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:35.19,0:21:39.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hm? Tubuh ini boleh juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.59,0:21:50.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ternyata kamu ada di sini
Dialogue: 10,0:21:51.50,0:21:53.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Satan.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:53.00,0:21:58.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku menemukanmu, Yuri!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:58.75,0:22:03.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Shiro!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:34.95,0:01:37.63,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Malam Biru pun dimulai.
